Description: # Lucene way search in django
        #### ("Django" AND "DRF") OR ("Elasticserach-DSL" AND "Django Rest Elasticsearch")
        
        _________________
        
        ## Installation
        
        Only for Django with DRF:
        
        ```
        pip install lusya
        ```
        
        For Django with DRF and Elasticsearch-dsl with DRF:
        
        ```
        pip install lucyfer
        ```
        
        ## Dependencies
        
        |                           | lucyfer | lusya |
        |---------------------------|---------|-------|
        | lucyparser                | +       | +     |
        | Django                    | +       | +     |
        | djangorestframework       | +       | +     |
        | django-rest-elasticsearch | +       | -     |
        | elasticsearch-dsl         | +       | -     |
        
        
